---
// src/components/VisualProof.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-blue-600 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm mb-3">The Chassis</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        First, we build the <br>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500">Perfect Digital Vessel.</span>
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        You can't win a Formula 1 race in a minivan. Before we deploy the Signal Engine, 
        we replace your slow, template-based site with a <strong>Performance Asset</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      
      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-blue-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold mb-4">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
              Core Web Vitals: Passed
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Instant Velocity.</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Google hates slow websites. We engineer yours to load in under <strong>100ms</strong>. 
              This isn't just "fast" - it's instant. This alone boosts your rank before we even touch SEO.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="shrink-0 relative w-40 h-40 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-full h-full transform -rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
              <path class="text-slate-200" d="M18 2.0845 a 15.9155 15.9155 0 0 1 0 31.831 a 15.9155 15.9155 0 0 1 0 -31.831" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" />
              <path class="text-green-500 drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(34,197,94,0.5)]" stroke-dasharray="100, 100" d="M18 2.0845 a 15.9155 15.9155 0 0 1 0 31.831 a 15.9155 15.9155 0 0 1 0 -31.831" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" />
            </svg>
            <div class="absolute text-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 block">100</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Performance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden text-white flex flex-col justify-between group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#60a5fa 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 20px 20px;"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <i data-lucide="crown" class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-400 mb-4"></i>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Premium Authority.</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We don't do "templates." We build bespoke interfaces that make you look like the market leader.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
           <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">S.</div>
              <div class="h-2 w-20 bg-white/20 rounded-full"></div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-600 rounded-3xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden text-white flex flex-col justify-center group hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h4 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-2 tracking-tight">+40%</h4>
          <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm font-medium mb-6">Average Conversion Lift</p>
          <p class="text-blue-200 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            A faster, prettier site doesn't just rank better - it sells better. We engineer layouts that guide visitors to the "Buy" button.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 group hover:border-blue-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="flex-1 order-2 md:order-1">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Clean Code Architecture.</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            No WordPress bloat. No plugins breaking every week. We build on the same modern tech stack used by Google, Porsche, and The Guardian.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 opacity-60 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">
             <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/BvbyKp31/stegg-logo.png" class="h-6 w-auto" alt="Astro" />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-64 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-xl transform rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform order-1 md:order-2">
          <div class="flex gap-1.5 mb-3">
            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <div class="h-2 w-16 bg-purple-400 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
            <div class="h-2 w-32 bg-blue-400 rounded-full opacity-50 pl-4"></div>
            <div class="h-2 w-24 bg-green-400 rounded-full opacity-50 pl-8"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>